          "slidetitle": "Calculating the True Cost",
          "subtitle": "Beyond the obvious financial impact",
          "slidecontent": "• Every false positive wastes materials, labour, and machine time on a product that was never actually faulty\n• Reputation damage when customers lose trust in your quality process\n• False negatives carry liability risk\n• Rework and reinspection cycles compound costs quickly across high-volume production lines\n• Hidden overhead from over-inspection, including staff time spent reviewing flagged items that pass on second check",
