        {
          "number": 6,
          "slidetitle": "Calculating the True Cost",
          "subtitle": "Beyond the obvious financial impact",
          "slidecontent": "• Every false positive wastes materials, labour, and machine time on a product that was actually fine\n• Rework and reinspection add hidden costs that rarely appear on a single defect report\n• Customer trust erodes slowly\n• False negatives carry liability risks, recall expenses, and potential regulatory penalties\n• Tracking both error types separately reveals where your AI model needs retraining or threshold adjustment",
          "do_not_include": true
        },
